text: Jean Louisa Kelly (born March 9, 1972) is an American actress and singer. She played Tia Russell in Uncle Buck, a 1989 comedy-drama movie. She later acted in Mr. Holland's Opus (1995). From 2000 to 2006, Kelly played Kim Warner in CBS' sitcom Yes, Dear. Kelly also guest starred in shows, like Mad About You, Cold Feet and Burn Notice.
